From f033c5773992dfa57b6657f10f53f719664a5f18 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Ilya Gulya <ilya@gulya.me>
Date: Sun, 12 Jul 2026 15:46:48 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] xnu: complete E-UNION syscall coverage and hardening

Consolidate write-site wiring, template protection, metadata and xattr policy, nested lower roots, and syscall edge-case handling on top of the E-UNION core.

Keep the behavior and regression fixtures of the existing series while removing chronology-only patch boundaries.
